@lovepoem 
1、CodecSupport.deserialize 反序列化 is ，当序列化工具使用分片读流时，若RpcResult的序列化byte大于分片值时，将引起is的startIndex变动。比如fst工具：org.nustaq.serialization.util.FSTInputStream 默认使用 8000 byte 分片读取is。

2、result.decode() 这时在反序列is。若startIndex产生变动，将引起RpcResult 读取到的序列化byte不正确。最终可能产生 #3537 issue。

We plan to use JWT(json web token) to implement authorization.We provide a auth service taking auth information from registry center. And user can set auth rules in a dashboard for auth service. We provide also a filter for consumer to get token from auth service and a provider check token with a filter.
Proceed as follow:
a.Consumer get token from Auth Service when it has no token or token is expire;
b.Auth Service check consumer information and provide token. Token is encrypted by provider's secret;
c.Consumer add token in attachment and send to provider;
d.Provider check token and return response.

